author: perrotta
body:
#### PR description:

The static analyzer is pointing to some unused code and dead initializations

While fixing them, I hit an obvious bug in [previous L452](https://github.com/cms-sw/cmssw/compare/master...perrotta:fixesAndDeadCodeRemovalInDqmL1tmonitor?expand=1#diff-470dd32c301a7da46a79b6f0756e5a56f3140495f393bf6bac1306a35b0e630cL452) of  DQM/L1TMonitor/src/L1TBPTX.cc where the numerator was filled twice, and none the numerator.

This makes me wonder whether this code was ever used... Anyhow, here is the fix.


#### PR validation:

It builds
title: Remove dead code and apply one fix in DQM/L1TMonitor
